    "Senior Managers accounted for 13.5% (47 respondents), Executive Managers made up 11.0% (38 respondents), and Directors and Representatives each represented 1.2% (4 respondents each) of the total sample.",
    "The distribution across different demographics not only provides a comprehensive view of the use of ChatGPT among workers but also allows for comparison across different groups, thus enhancing the generalizability of the study's findings.",
